Introduction.Title: No Description Available
Introduction.Content: A mysterious Resonator with the power to absorb all sounds. Currently journeying to find their lost memories.

Tags.TagDesc: Slows down targets within a certain range

Skins.Name: Wandering Traveler
Skins.BgDescription: Rover's usual outfit. This is what he wore at the beginning of his journey and what he will be wearing for the rest of it.

Skills.SkillDescribe:
Basic Attack

Rover performs up to 4 consecutive attacks, dealing Spectro DMG.


Heavy Attack

Rover consumes STA to attack the target, dealing Spectro DMG.


Heavy Attack: Resonance

After Basic Attack 3 or Heavy Attack, press the Basic Attack button at the right time to perform Heavy Attack Resonance, dealing Spectro DMG.


Heavy Attack: Aftertune

After Heavy Attack Resonance or Dodge Counter hits a target, press the Basic Attack button to perform Heavy Attack Aftertune, dealing Spectro DMG.


Mid-air Attack

Rover consumes STA to perform a Mid-Air Plunging Attack, dealing Spectro DMG.


Dodge Counter

Use Basic Attack after a successful Dodge to attack the target, dealing Spectro DMG.
Rover launches an attack forward, dealing Spectro DMG.
Rover converges Spectro energy to assail the target area, detonating it after a short delay and dealing Spectro DMG.
DMG dealt by Rover's Basic Attack Resonating Echoes is increased by 60%.
Rover gains 15% ATK increase for 5s upon casting Heavy Attack Resonance.
Rover attacks the target, dealing Spectro DMG.

Skills.SkillName: World in a Grain of Sand
Skills.SkillDescribe:
Resonance Skill: Resonating Spin

If "Diminutive Sound" exceeds 50 when Resonance Skill is used, Rover consumes 50 "Diminutive Sound" to cast Resonating Spin, dealing Spectro DMG, considered as Resonance Skill DMG.


Basic Attack: Resonating Echoes

After Resonance Skill Resonating Spin ends, Rover performs Resonating Echoes upon using Basic Attack button.
Launch attacks forward, dealing Spectro DMG, considered as Resonance Skill DMG.


Diminutive Sound

Rover can hold up to 100 "Diminutive Sounds".
Rover obtains "Diminutive Sound" for every Normal Attack Vibration Manifestation on hit.
Rover obtains "Diminutive Sound" for every Heavy Attack Aftertune on hit.
Rover obtains "Diminutive Sound" upon casting Intro Skill Waveshock.
Generate an area of stasis centered around the incoming Resonator, lasting for 3s.
Channel Spectro energy to attack the target area, causing a blast after a short delay, dealing Spectro DMG and applying 6 stack(s) of Spectro Frazzle.

Resonance Skill: Resonating Spin

If "Diminutive Sound" exceeds 50 when Resonance Skill is used, consume 50 "Diminutive Sound" to cast Resonating Spin, dealing Spectro DMG. This DMG is considered as Resonance Skill DMG and applies 2 stack(s) of Spectro Frazzle along with Shimmer.


Shimmer

Shimmer prevents Spectro Frazzle stacks from reducing over time.


Basic Attack: Resonating Echoes

After Resonance Skill Resonating Spin ends, follow up with Basic Attack to cast Resonating Echoes.
Launch forward to attack the enemies, dealing Spectro DMG, considered as Resonance Skill DMG.


Diminutive Sound

Rover can hold up to 100 "Diminutive Sounds".
Rover obtains "Diminutive Sound" for every Normal Attack Vibration Manifestation on hit.
Rover obtains "Diminutive Sound" for every Heavy Attack Aftertune on hit.
Rover obtains "Diminutive Sound" upon casting Intro Skill Waveshock.

ResonantChain.AttributesDescription: Rover's Crit. Rate is increased by 15% for 7s when casting Resonance Skill Resonating Slashes or Resonance Skill Resonating Spin.
Rover's Spectro DMG Bonus is increased by 20%.
Rover's Energy Regen is increased by 20%.
When casting Resonance Liberation Echoing Resonance, Rover continuously restores HP for all team members: HP equal to 20% of Rover's ATK will be restored every second for 5s.
Rover's Resonance Liberation DMG Bonus is increased by 40%.
Resonance Skill Resonating Slashes and Resonance Skill Resonating Spin reduces the target's Spectro RES by 10% on hit for 20s.

Words.Title: Idle: II
Words.Content: This is a testament to my connection with the world around me, and it's very much my companion now, bearing witness to everything I've experienced on this journey.

Words.Title: Idle: III
Words.Content: It is natural to feel dreadful of the unknown, yet... there are times when the unknown harbors hope, like how I can never know what else this power has to offer.

Words.Title: Join Team: I
Words.Content: We still have a long journey ahead of us. Let's press on.

Words.Title: Join Team: III
Words.Content: I will be there for everyone... As we head toward our shared future, leaving the past behind.

Words.Title: Ascension: I
Words.Content: The world around me... I can hear it clearer now.

Words.Title: Ascension: II
Words.Content: This power... it's mysterious, yet reassuring nonetheless.

Words.Title: Ascension: III
Words.Content: I still need more time to acquaint myself with this unfamiliar world.

Words.Title: Ascension: IV
Words.Content: A new journey awaits? Brimming with novel sounds, stories, and... fragmented memories.

Words.Title: Ascension: V
Words.Content: The place where the land ends is where the ocean begins. Our journey is far from ending.

DescList: Normal Attack, Resonance Skill and Intro Skill recover Forte Gauge on hit
Cast enhanced Resonance Skill when Forte Gauge is above 50%

InputDetails.description: Resonating Spin: When Forte Gauge reaches 50, use
Resonating Echoes: Perform Resonating Spin and use
Heavy Attack - Resonance: After Basic Attack Stage 3 or Heavy Attack, at the right time
Heavy Attack: Aftertune: Tap after Heavy Attack: Resonance hits a target
